headline.print_headline: Euro 2016 Qualifiers Likely to Be a Damp Squib
headline.main: Euro 2016 Qualifiers Likely to Be a Damp Squib

lead_paragraph: Two wins in 10 matches could be enough to reach Euro 2016 following UEFA’s decision to expand the final tournament to 24 teams while keeping the same format for the qualifying competition.
